  4. Added Rain_Rate_clicks parameter in record retrieval

  5. Minor documentation updates. Closes #91709

  6. Updated README file


Ver 0.23  Tue Apr 20 2010
  1. Added Device::SerialPort to PREREQ_PM in Makefile.PM
 
  2. Fixed bug in unpacking UV_MAX changed from s to C

